data.description: DREAMING OF AN INTEREST RATE in the 5% RANGE? ASK about the Assumable VA Loan with NAVY FEDERAL; must qualify (doesn't have to be a veteran). Although this is not the only financing option, seller is willing to BUY DOWN THE RATE to 5.5% the first year and 6.5% second year. Ask your agent for info. Sitting on ALMOST HALF AN ACRE LOT with LAKE ACCESS in your backyard!  3 bedroom 2 bath - main level living with unfinished basement. 4 sides brick and vinyl trim, no maintenance. Totally remodeled - ask your agent for the complete list!  EVERYTHING has been updated - paint, flooring, windows, exterior siding, NEW kitchen and NEW bathrooms, New Appliances, lighting - including switches and plugs, ductwork, landscaping, tree removal, and fence added.  Pictures don't do it justice, see it for yourself.   This was to a be a forever home with much care invested here, but job relocation happened. Great location - near Homestead Hollow - 2.5 miles to I59.
